commit.message:
Split the ocaml filetype into several filetypes

Now ocamlinterface ocamllex and menhir types must be taken into account
as well. Menhir filetype is not included as there seem to be no plans to
include it and even then it would take a big effort.

The filetypes are introduced by
https://github.com/ocaml/vim-ocaml/pull/61

commit.message:
Simplify args logic inside run_in_directory

Feedback from @nojb
outfile option in ml_merlin_system_command
Include standalone [ppx.exe] in Win32 no-shell fixes

Fix `FLG -pp ppx.exe -as-pp/-dump-ast` on Windows

Windows is special cased in Merlin to have a direct
program execution without any shell, so shell redirection
does not work.

This is a narrow, Windows-only fix for
https://github.com/ocaml/merlin/issues/1722
